{
  "stem": "11552.4",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What happened then, it went into January, and word went around that the Germans are being defeated in the Eastern Front, and that the Russians were coming.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then one time in February, a contingency of Russian partisans passed that village, and the villagers thought that that was the Russians coming, but they were just partisans.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it made them afraid to-- to look for Jews, or kill, because they shouldn't pay later on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Not that anybody paid for killing Jews, but that-- that they assumed that somebody's going to punish them for their murders.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My life continued until March, and then we were liberated in March.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Russians came into that area.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very hungry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I used to eat grass.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and I ate flowers, if there were any flowers blooming, I ate flowers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was-- my stomach must've shrunk to-- to very little.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But some people, when I went, I always asked for work first, before I begged.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I used to milk cows, I used to clean the stables, I used to do any-- I-- I-- I did everything possible.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother stayed in one place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, my mother, I could never let her go out in the village.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My mother was very, very beautiful.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She had this black hair, white skin, and violet eyes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nobody in the village looked like my mother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was very obvious that this was not a Polish or Ukrainian woman.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She was just too beautiful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Not that-- please don't get me wrong, not that Ukrainian and Polish women were not beautiful, she was just not a village woman.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I beg your pardon?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I hid my mother.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I never let her go out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I brought it to her.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
